//for the test to work, replace the fake email with your registered one
### 1. Request Password Reset Code (Should trigger email)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "elene@gmail.com"
}

### 2. Submit New Password (Replace the code below with the real one)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "elene@gmail.com",
  "code": "123456",
  "newPassword": "newSecurePassword123"
}

### 3. Verify Login with New Password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "elene@gmail.com",
  "password": "newSecurePassword123"
}